  <h2>Before you connect</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Use a recent photo and a name you're comfortable with.</li>
    <li>Don't share your home address, workplace, or financial info.</li>
    <li>Trust your gut — if something feels off, it probably is.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Meeting up IRL</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Pick a public place for first meets — a café, a park, a busy spot.</li>
    <li>Tell a friend where you're going and when you'll check in.</li>
    <li>Arrange your own transport. Don't rely on the other person.</li>
    <li>Stay sober enough to leave whenever you want.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Red flags</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Someone asking for money, gifts, or financial help.</li>
    <li>Pressure to move off Duncit to another platform too quickly.</li>
    <li>Inconsistent stories or refusing to video chat.</li>
    <li>Anyone making you uncomfortable — block, report, move on.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Need help?</h2>
  <p>Visit <a href="/safety/resources">our resources page</a> for crisis hotlines, or email <a href="mailto:safety@duncit.com">safety@duncit.com</a>.</p>
</PageLayout>
